  <CalDefinition Description="VP2 IMAGE ADJUSTMENT REGISTER; Note as defined in the TW8845 data sheet: FUNCTION: SH_FREQ; DESCRIPTION: Sharpness frequency select; 1 = High Frequency, and  0 = Low Frequency. Also, note as reference: a value of True = 1, and a value of False = 0. " Name="TW8845_WITH_DIGITAL_CAMERA_REGISTER_0x88C_BIT7" References="TECHWELL TW8845 Data Sheet" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
