  <CalDefinition Description="VP2 IMAGE ADJUSTMENT REGISTER; Note as defined in the TW8845 data sheet: FUNCTION: BPY2R; DESCRIPTION: Bypass YCbCr conversion to RGB; 1 = Bypass conversion, and  0 = Convert YCbCr to RGB.  Also, note as reference: a value of True = 1, and a value of False = 0.  " Name="TW8845_WITH_DIGITAL_CAMERA_REGISTER_0x8BE_BIT2" References="TECHWELL TW8845 Data Sheet" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
